PN,31601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FPassengers evacuated from a cruise
OL,7,Fship hit by a hantavirus outbreak are
OL,8,Fspending their first night at an
OL,9,Fisolation facility after being
OL,10,Frepatriated from Tenerife.
OL,12,FA chartered Titan Airways flight
OL,13,Ftransported the passengers from the
OL,14,FCanary Islands to Manchester Airport
OL,15,Fon Sunday evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FTwenty British passengers, who were
OL,7,Ftested for hantavirus before getting
OL,8,Fon the flight, were taken to isolate
OL,9,Fat the UK's initial Covid quarantine
OL,10,Fsite at Arrowe Park Hospital on the
OL,11,FWirral, Merseyside.
OL,13,FOne German national, who is a UK
OL,14,Fresident, and one Japanese passenger
OL,15,Ffrom the MV Hondius cruise ship are
OL,16,Falso being monitored at Arrowe Park.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FThe UK Government took the Japanese
OL,7,Fpassenger at the request of the Tokyo
OL,8,Fgovernment and they will complete
OL,9,Ftheir isolation in the UK in line with
OL,10,FUK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,11,Fguidance.
OL,13,FStrict infection control measures were
OL,14,Fin place throughout the journey to
OL,15,FArrowe Park, with passengers, crew,
OL,16,Fdrivers and medical teams all wearing
OL,17,Fpersonal protective equipment such as
OL,18,Fface masks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FWithin a 72-hour period, the
OL,7,Fpassengers will receive clinical
OL,8,Fassessments and testing at the
OL,9,Fisolation facility.
OL,11,FThe Arrowe Park site has six storeys
OL,12,Fof self-contained flats with their own
OL,13,Fbedrooms, en-suite bathrooms, kitchen
OL,14,Fand lounge facilities.
OL,16,FJanelle Holmes, chief executive of
OL,17,FWirral University Teaching Hospital
OL,18,FNHS Foundation Trust, told the media
OL,19,Fthat Arrowe Park would carry out
OL,20,F"welfare checks on each individual".
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FShe added: "There's nobody being
OL,7,Ftransferred to us that has been
OL,8,Fsymptomatic in any way.
OL,10,F"There's no impact on the hospital.
OL,11,FServices are running as normal,
OL,12,Fpatients should still attend their
OL,13,Fappointments."
OL,15,FThe hospital leader said if passengers
OL,16,Fdevelop symptoms, they will be taken
OL,17,Fto Royal Liverpool University
OL,18,FHospital, which houses the regional
OL,19,FTropical and Infectious Diseases Unit.
OL,26,@nD@LOUrD@AOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FMs Holmes said hantavirus is "very
OL,7,Fdifferent" to Covid and the risk to
OL,8,Fthe general public is "really low".
OL,10,FShe added: "You've got to have really,
OL,11,Freally close contact. It's not like
OL,12,FCovid or flu or those types of
OL,13,Fviruses."
OL,15,FDuring the 72-hour period at Arrowe
OL,16,FPark, public health specialists will
OL,17,Fassess whether passengers can isolate
OL,18,Fat home or at another suitable
OL,19,Flocation based on their living
OL,20,Farrangements.
OL,26,@nD@^OUoD@JO]pD@WOUpD@bO]rD@LOUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FBritons returning to the UK will stay
OL,7,Fin self-isolation for 45 days and will
OL,8,Fnot be allowed to take public
OL,9,Ftransport to their homes.
OL,11,FDuring their isolation period,
OL,12,Fpassengers will have daily contact
OL,13,Fwith UKHSA health protection teams to
OL,14,Fcheck on their wellbeing and ensure
OL,15,Fthey are supported to isolate safely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FProfessor Robin May, chief scientific
OL,7,Fofficer at the agency, said:"We are
OL,8,Fpleased to confirm that all British
OL,9,Fnationals onboard the MV Hondius have
OL,10,Fnow safely returned to the UK and are
OL,11,Fbeing supported by UKHSA and NHS
OL,12,Fmedical experts at Arrowe Park, who
OL,13,Fhave worked at pace to prepare for the
OL,14,Fsafe arrival of passengers at the
OL,15,Ffacility.
OL,17,F"Staff at Arrowe Park have once again
OL,18,Fdemonstrated their commitment and
OL,19,Fprofessionalism in responding rapidly
OL,20,Fto a health emergency, and we are very
OL,21,Fgrateful.
OL,26,@oD@^OUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,F"The risk remains very low for members
OL,7,Fof the general public."
OL,9,FPublic health minister Sharon Hodgson
OL,10,Fsaid: "None of the passengers are
OL,11,Fsymptomatic but we will monitor them
OL,12,Fclosely over the next 72 hours at the
OL,13,Fhospital, as part of a precautionary
OL,14,Fisolation period.
OL,16,F"With no cases or symptoms among them
OL,17,Fand both our stringent monitoring and
OL,18,Fisolation measures, the risk to the
OL,19,Fpublic remains extremely low."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@WO]rD@GOUxD@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FIn a post on X, Foreign Secretary
OL,7,FYvette Cooper said: "Thank you to all
OL,8,Fthose who worked around the clock to
OL,9,Fget passengers from MV Hondius back to
OL,10,Fthe UK by special flight this evening
OL,11,Fwith public health protections in
OL,12,Fplace.
OL,14,F"The UK has worked with Spain, South
OL,15,FAfrica, the Netherlands and the WHO to
OL,16,Fcoordinate safe returns."
OL,26,@oD@UOUvD@AOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FThe MV Hondius arrived in Tenerife on
OL,7,FSunday morning, with Spanish
OL,8,Fauthorities beginning evacuations of
OL,9,Fthe cruise ship by nationality and
OL,10,Fferrying passengers to a port by small
OL,11,Fboat.
OL,13,FWhile they were being bussed from the
OL,14,Fport at Granadilla de Abona to
OL,15,FTenerife South Airport, some British
OL,16,Fpassengers, clad in blue PPE, waved
OL,17,Fand gave thumbs up as they passed
OL,18,Fwatching media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FThe World Health Organisation (WHO)
OL,7,Fsaid its goal was to finish the ship's
OL,8,Fevacuation, with the exception of 30
OL,9,Fcrew members remaining on board, by
OL,10,F7pm on Monday.
OL,12,FPassengers were told to leave their
OL,13,Fluggage on the ship and were only
OL,14,Fallowed to take a small bag with
OL,15,Fessential items such as their phone
OL,16,Fand passport.
OL,18,FThe Spanish health ministry said on
OL,19,FSunday that 94 people of 19
OL,20,Fnationalities had been taken off the
OL,21,Fcruise ship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FOne of five French passengers showed
OL,7,Fsymptoms during their repatriation
OL,8,Fflight, French Prime Minister
OL,9,FSebastien Lecornu said on Sunday.
OL,11,FIn a post on X, he said all five were
OL,12,F"immediately placed in strict
OL,13,Fisolation until further notice" where
OL,14,Fthey will receive medical care and
OL,15,Fundergo further testing.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FThe 30 crew members and a nurse from
OL,7,Fthe Netherlands, as well as the body
OL,8,Fof a passenger who died on board, will
OL,9,Fremain on the ship, which will sail to
OL,10,FRotterdam in the Netherlands where it
OL,11,Fwill undergo disinfection, the WHO
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe WHO said on Saturday there had
OL,15,Fbeen six confirmed hantavirus cases
OL,16,Flinked to MV Hondius and four patients
OL,17,Fwere in hospital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FIt added that eight cases, including
OL,7,Fthree deaths, had been reported ` with
OL,8,Fone previous suspected case being
OL,9,Freclassified after testing negative
OL,10,Ffor hantavirus.
OL,12,FThe UK Health Security Agency said
OL,13,Fthree British nationals are included
OL,14,Fin the eight cases ` two involve
OL,15,Fconfirmed hantavirus and another is
OL,16,Fsuspected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FThe two confirmed British cases are in
OL,7,Fhospital in South Africa and the
OL,8,FNetherlands, while the third British
OL,9,Fnational with a suspected case is
OL,10,Fbeing supported on the British
OL,11,Foverseas territory of Tristan da Cunha
OL,12,Fwhere they live.
OL,14,FSix paratroopers, an RAF consultant
OL,15,Fand an Army nurse from 16 Air Assault
OL,16,FBrigade were parachuted on to the
OL,17,FSouth Atlantic island, while oxygen
OL,18,Fsupplies and medical aid were also
OL,19,Fdropped on Tristan da Cunha, which is
OL,20,Fnormally only accessible by boat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778519160
OL,3,CPassengers from hantavirus-hit ship
OL,4,Cspend first night at isolation facility
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Defence said it was
OL,7,Fthe first time medical personnel had
OL,8,Fbeen parachuted in to provide
OL,9,Fhumanitarian support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
